<a href="/questions/568712-i-m-searching-for-a-quotation-related-to">I&#39;m searching for a quotation related to conversations and egos in Conversation in the Cathedral. It should look like &quot;when there is a conversation, it&#39;s a confrontation of egos and one wants to dominate the other&quot;. Any idea? Thanks!</a>
