<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Are confusing dialogues, overlapped. Untidy. Created inside a bar, in Lima, Peru. Probably under influence of alcohol. It should shade your curiosity.<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Are confusing dialogues, overlapped. Untidy. Created inside a bar, in Lima, Peru. Probably under influence of alcohol. It should shade your curiosity. [...] In the context, is described a general illusion of people losers: a lack of vision of their rights, because of an ineffective government.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
